Version 1.0.0-pre.6 / License MIT / Copyright (c) 2024 Edmund Hung

A type-safe form validation library utilizing web fundamentals to progressively enhance HTML Forms, delivering a modern, accessible, and resilient user experience with full support for server frameworks like Remix actions and Next.js server actions.

> Getting Started

Check out the tutoiral at https://conform.guide/tutoiral for a quick overview.

> Documentation

The documentation is divided into several sections:

* Overview: https://conform.guide/overview
* Example Usages: https://conform.guide/examples
* Complex structures: https://conform.guide/complex-structures
* UI Integrations: https://conform.guide/integrations
* Accessibility Guide: https://conform.guide/accessibility
* API Reference: https://conform.guide/references

> Support

To report a bug, please open an issue on the GitHub repository at https://github.com/edmundhung/conform. For feature requests and questions, you can post them in the Discussions section.
